Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:18.34,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0015,,{\blur3}I have a big gun, I took it from my Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:21.79,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sick with Justice, I just wanna feel you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.20,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm your angel, only a ring away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:28.55,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You make me violate you, no matter who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's all up to you, no one lives forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:42.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Been burn in the hell, by all those pigs out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:45.53,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's always been hell, from when I was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:48.72,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}They make me violate them, no matter who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:52.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs79}Get down on your knees! Get a good head on your shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:55.69,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}If it's for your guys, go to the end of the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:59.00,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Do what you think, give it with dedication...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:02.27,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'll put out your misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:05.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You made a mess! For Christ sakes, this rotten world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:09.10,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Shit out of luck! Go with my vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:12.54,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Light up the fire! Right on the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:15.90,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:24.48,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you finished getting changed,\Nbig sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We won't be coming back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's gather what we need and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, big brother.\NPlease become big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.14,0:02:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go, big sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget our tickets\Nand passports.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. Without them,\Nwe can't go anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.52,0:02:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and they won't let us\Nthrough anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let us be\Non our way, big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Yes. That's precisely it.\NThat's what reminded me. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Rock.\NI'll be sure to return the favor sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock was able to give me the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kids are from\NCount Dracula's home country.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're Romanian.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Romanian!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Romanian troops at Kabul\Nwere speaking similar words.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've known.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, as people get older, remembering\Nthings becomes quite the task.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it, Sergeant.\NIt's the same with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant. Rowan, the owner of\Nthe pink shop on Rachiada Street...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...secretly sells illegal videos,\Ndoesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he does.\NWhat about Rowan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got rid of unwanted company,\Nhave you, Chang?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a delicate meeting. It would\Nbe so much nicer if this were a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't enjoy a matinée with the\Nsmell of blood lingering, now can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chang, we now know who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:05:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an intriguing subject.\NHow'd you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we found out what we\Nneeded from an item Rowan sells.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rowan, the porn shop guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You called him to your office?\NHe must've been scared as hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough to create a masterpiece\Nin his pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an unfortunate man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I demanded from him\Nwas kiddie porn...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or a snuff film starring\NRomanian twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came up with 250 titles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, very unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tackled those 250 made-for-pervert\Nvideos all night and half the next day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then finally, bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hansel and Gretel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what they were\Ncalled in the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.94,0:05:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Following the change of government\Nin Romania...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...many children were sold\Nto the black market...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...by facilities that could no longer\Ntake care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Illegitimate children of the dead dictator.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treated like toys by sick perverts, they\Neventually ended up as food for the pigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.46,0:06:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how were these kids, destined for\Nthe same fate, able to get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For entertainment, the sick fools decided\Nto let them take part in some killings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killings of sacrificed children\Nmuch like themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to survive\Nfrom one night to the next...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...these kids desperately learned\Nhow to kill in ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that would please the perverts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And over time, the kids\Nwould come to accept all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They left the world of blue skies\Nand fell into the pitch-black shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stunt dogs for video entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a brutal story.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It suits our world perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I sometimes feel\NI'm walking on this huge piece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff like morality and justice\Njust don't suit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:07:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Words like that are surprisingly similar\Nto the stuff that comes outta your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have about the same amount\Nof sympathy for those kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as I have for the idiots selling missiles\Nwhile preaching about peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm merely telling you what I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no need for justice.\NAll we need is profit and trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we got to Rowan,\Nthe rest was simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So this is where it came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having their own killed does work\Nas a perfect alibi, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were intended for show.\NIt's not as if they ever learned manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They scatter trouble and create shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your men just happened to\Nget caught in the blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the reason,\Nthey're gonna have to pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.26,0:07:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They only have to get rid of\Nthat lady fox...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...yet they keep adding\Nunwanted dead bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Boss.\N- Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we just call it quits?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we stop now, we could still get away...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...by saying we got rid of the nut job\Nthat wreaked havoc in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're gonna get rid of those kids\Nwithout causing a commotion...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...now would be the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare a petty underling like you\Ntalk back to your boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Boss! They're too much to handle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we called those damn kids\Nover here in the first place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree it's about time\Nto change the color of this city, Chang?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There'd no longer be a purpose\Nfor the information sessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna start another war?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather you refer to it as a controlled\Nconflict. We have reason and motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a war with a just cause. I never\Nthought of you as the type for pretty talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's simply a matter of whether or not\Nit works as an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have the dogs chew on\Nwhether or not it's just.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Join us or forget about it.\NIt's your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something I should need to\Nconsult my country about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one and only thing that can\Nbe trusted in this world is power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean we'll be seeing\Nthe gunman within you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't dislike standing in\Nthe gaming room...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but right now I have a position\Nto protect. Such a drag.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and one other thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me "Babe".\NI hate that nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Captain?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant. Chang has agreed\Nto our suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As of this moment, we will form a\Ncommon front with the Hong Kong Triad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Roger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send a message\Nto our fellow comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Standby for assumed battle,\Nfrom nineteen-o-five hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Recite "Regulation 217, Case Five".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Standby for assumed battle,\Nfrom nineteen-o-five hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A snatch mission within the city's\Ncontrolled battlegrounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Correct.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos is to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city is like a festival with everyone\Ntrying to get their hands on the reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The festive spirit{\i0}\N{\i1}is a good thing, Captain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the better if it comes from{\i0}\N{\i1}the sound of bullets being fired.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're right about that, Sergeant.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only type of war we can\Nbe involved in right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll deal with it with respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the Bosses of Palermo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have expressed an interest\Nin this damn, boring city!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're fed up with me because\NI haven't been able to take control!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen very carefully,\Nyou damn bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless I do something about it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you know what will happen to me\Nat the next meeting of the top brass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Damn it!\N- Um... Um, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Shut up!\N- But... Um... the twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Those kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I thought I told you not to come here!\NWhat are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us talked it over,\Nand made a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.05,0:11:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have borscht for our main dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start with macaroni.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't mess with me\Ny-you damn brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the macaroni\Nis thoroughly boiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna die now, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Chang. We've completely\Nsurrounded the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll move in as soon as\Nyou give the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be wise to keep your head low.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our job has just been\Nchanged to hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact Hotel Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do them a favor\Nthey'll feel obliged to pay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Revy. The police are on the move.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're about to close off\Nthe main street.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There appears to have been some\Nmovement around the Verrocchio family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy! We'll never reach the prize\Nfrom the bleachers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Stop shouting, Eda.\NSo, where do we meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Joey got a room at the Palcana Square.{\i0}\N{\i1}Get here quickly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy. The blasting fuse has been lit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no stopping the bomb\Nfrom exploding now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All units, attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fellow comrades. Earlier tonight,\Nthe Verrocchio Family was assaulted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there are no changes\Nto our plan. We expected this to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We commence our plan now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brave fellow comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Sakharov and Corporal Menshov\Nwere very special comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will light the sacred light of repose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The souls of our passed comrades will\Nturn our guns into a goddess of revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the judgment of our Kalashnikovs,\Ntear apart their gills...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.76,0:13:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with your 5.45-millimeter AK-47s!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Chang.\NA message from Hotel Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We have a dangerous situation.\NRetreat at once."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, it's too late now. Cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duck!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad!\NYou're pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately we don't have the time\Nto be dealing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The source of the fire is\Nthe Verrocchio Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.55,0:14:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watsap is questioning the Triad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This route is now much\Ncloser to the gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the opening\Nof a Carnival Night Party.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hallelujah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. It's a Japanese-make\Nblack sedan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if they get rid of the car,\Nwe'll have no way of knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter.\NShoot anyone who passes by.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't push!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.94,0:15:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Eda?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just realized a moment ago.\NThere's something odd about this, Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?\NStop beating around the bush.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Balalaika.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one in this world that\Nwants revenge more than that lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...yet she hasn't appeared on this street.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, come to think of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this were really where it's going down,\Nwe'd be shut out of here by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where would those twins go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're two kids with no logic...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.74,0:15:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but if they were after anyone,\Nit'd be Balalaika herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything else would be a feint...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or rather a stopover\Nto get to their destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Balalaika got the Visotonikis moving so\Nthat she could fuck those twins herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The soldiers are all pragmatists.\NThey won't act on speculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The twins will try to outwit them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's treating this like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they're hunting deer\Nin the mountains of Montana.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But these are no deer. The twins\Nare coyotes. They won't be easy prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they were the type to get their asses\Nstuck in this kinda trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they'd have been\Nresting below a tombstone long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You catch on quickly for someone\Nwith no education, Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, which alley will get us\Nto Hotel Moscow quickest from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Through the Chalquam Market and\Nstraight along Saatanam Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you have no education either,\Nyou lust demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry for your loss, Chang.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd have known those kids were there,\NI would've brought some of my top guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine, I've gotta walk home now.\NThis is too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, right. I took care of Watsap for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I figured you could do without him{\i0}\N{\i1}in your way...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:17:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...so I sent him off to nowhere{\i0}\N{\i1}on a hunting spree.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can pay me back later somehow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly have all the angles covered.\NI owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's going according to plan\Non our end, Chang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.15,0:17:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first march will commence\Nany time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! It's that car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake about it.\NIt's a Japanese-make black sedan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Are the twins in it?\N- I can't see through the tinted windows!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why wait to check? Blast 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we get 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kid isn't white!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one of the local kids!\NDamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- We missed! Shit!\N- Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watsap's headed south\Nfor the fishing port.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's where the catch is!\N- Bring the car around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll smoke those kids out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As we expected, right big sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having someone take over your identity\Nfor 5,000 baht? Now that's pretty cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I kinda feel sorry for him.\NHe said he was an orphan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be helped, big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You either kill or get killed in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.82,0:18:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, big brother.\NIt couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, big sister. So let's kill.\NLet's kill more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy located.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The squad behind Chalquam Street\Nhas located the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A diversionary attack\Nwas executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Which direction are they headed now?\N- East, as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should come to\NLadoga Point any time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Target has turned left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.05,0:19:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're proceeding\Nalong the course properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.45,0:19:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After Squad Three\Nopened fire on them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.69,0:20:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they left Ladoga Point and are now\Nheaded to Livinsk. We'll be standing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Send a squad over to Hamipon Street.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make certain there's only\None floodgate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have the squads retreat as soon as\Nthey've done their part.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their main objective\Nis to guide the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which squad was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not fully set up\Nin that direction yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.31,0:20:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be a hunter.\NAll units, report back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get rid of anyone who gets in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. Don't move, damn brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find yourself in trouble\Nroaming the streets this late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially tonight when\Nthe whole town is out on a manhunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.06,0:20:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really should think about\Nworshiping God more often.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the bounty being offered\Non our heads?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.04,0:20:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eighty grand. Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. That's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'd like to\Ndiscuss something with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.85,0:21:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have with me money I brought\Nfrom Verrocchio's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.59,0:21:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could go at it here, but there are\Nthings we wanna take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.19,0:21:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you accept 100,000\Nand pretend you never saw us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding me.\NI'm not gonna be used by some kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.43,0:21:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about 150,000?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Um, well, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Revy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you hesitating for, Eda?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.98,0:21:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,80 grand, 150 grand, {\i1}and{\i0} their lives!\NWe'll take it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've relocated the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.82,0:21:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chinese woman\Nfrom Lagoon Company...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.96,0:21:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the sister from\Nthe Ripoff Church are also there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.49,0:21:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have nothing to do with\Nour operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have to, crush them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.56,0:23:18.56,Black Lagoon Next Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10\pos(980,916)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of blood and rotten sewers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.91,0:23:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I are the same thing!
